        "id": 894710,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16256199. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #7 posted 08 Sep 2025 at 08:26 UTC_\n\n\n<p>Cover <span class=\"drupalorg-gitlab-issue-link project-issue-status-info project-issue-status-7\"><a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/canvas/issues/3545378\" title=\"Status: Closed (fixed)\">#3545378: Canvas AI: Agents fail due to missing entity type and entity ID parameters</a></span> in this issue. I believe that 'Should verify AI panel API request and response payload' could have prevented this problem.</p>",
