        "id": 894711,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16264479. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #9 posted 12 Sep 2025 at 22:09 UTC_\n\n\n> **File** [test.mp4](https://www.drupal.org/files/issues/2025-09-12/test.mp4) \n\n<p>I've added a Playwright test to cover component generation via the AI chat interface. The test confirms that:</p>\n<p>- The AI panel is accessible.<br>\n- Users can input a prompt (e.g., \"Create a hero banner component with a title and button\").<br>\n- The AI generates content in response.<br>\n- The generated component appears in the editor.</p>\n<p>Attachment: video demostration.</p>\n<p>Test file: `test-generate-component-with-ai.spec.ts`</p>\n<p>This contributes to expanding test coverage for the XB AI module as outlined in the issue.</p>",
