        "id": 894714,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16290263. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #12 posted 02 Oct 2025 at 20:41 UTC_\n\n\n> **File** [testPageCanva.mp4](https://www.drupal.org/files/issues/2025-10-02/testPageCanva.mp4) \n\n<p>This update extends test coverage by adding validation for page creation through the AI panel in Canvas.<br>\nThe test now simulates user interaction with the AI panel and verifies successful page generation.<br>\nSee attached video for visual proof of functionality.<br>\nReady for review! </p>",
        "author": {
            "id": 64156,
            "username": "jvbrian",
            "public_email": null,
            "name": "Brian Villamil",
            "state": "active",
            "locked": false,
            "avatar_url": "https://git.drupalcode.org/uploads/-/system/user/avatar/64156/picture-3769347-1687018177.jpg",
            "web_url": "https://git.drupalcode.org/jvbrian"
