    {
        "id": 894715,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16291593. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #13 posted 03 Oct 2025 at 21:52 UTC_\n\n\n> **File** [testComponent.mp4](https://www.drupal.org/files/issues/2025-10-03/testComponent.mp4) \n\n<p>This update adds a Playwright test to validate Canvas state tracking during AI-driven component workflows.<br>\nThe test covers component creation via the AI panel, addition to the component library, and insertion into the Canvas&mdash;verifying that current_layout and selected_component are correctly updated throughout.<br>\nSee attached video for a full demonstration of the test in action.<br>\nReady for review!</p>",
        "author": {
            "id": 64156,
            "username": "jvbrian",
            "public_email": null,
            "name": "Brian Villamil",
            "state": "active",
            "locked": false,
