    {
        "id": 894716,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16292761. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #14 posted 06 Oct 2025 at 09:01 UTC_\n\n\n```\n- Status: Active\n+ Status: Needs work\n\n```\n\n<p>Can you please create a merge request for this? This will automatically run the created test and make it easier to review.<br>\nAlso, I think these tests should not interact with the LLM directly; we should mock the response instead.<br>\nSee:- tests/src/Playwright/ai.spec.ts</p>",
