    {
        "id": 894717,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16326331. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #15 posted 29 Oct 2025 at 19:47 UTC_\n\n\n> **File** [CanvasEditor.mp4](https://www.drupal.org/files/issues/2025-10-29/CanvasEditor.mp4) \n\n<p>I have applied a fix to the CanvasEditor.spec.ts file because the ai.spec.ts test was throwing some errors, the settings are as follows:<br>\n- Wait for the editor UI.<br>\n- Detect the panel by stable data-testid instead of a &ldquo;Library&rdquo; heading.<br>\n- Do not click again if the panel is already open.<br>\n- Overlay reflects new instance count</p>",
        "author": {
            "id": 64156,
            "username": "jvbrian",
            "public_email": null,
            "name": "Brian Villamil",
            "state": "active",
            "locked": false,
