    {
        "id": 894718,
        "type": null,
        "body": "<!-- Migrated from comment CID #16334850. -->\n> _Migrated from comment #17 posted 05 Nov 2025 at 22:18 UTC_\n\n\n> **File** [test1.mp4](https://www.drupal.org/files/issues/2025-11-05/test1.mp4) \n\n<p>2 new tests are added to cover these scenarios:<br>\n- Page builder task<br>\n- Page history.</p>\n<p>pageBuilderTask.spec.ts<br>\nTests of basic AI functionalities in the page builder: answering questions, creating components, generating metadata and titles, and processing editing commands.</p>\n<p>pageHistory.spec.ts<br>\nAI History Persistence Tests: Verify that interactions are maintained across navigation, multiple queries, and page reloads.</p>\n<p>Both use fixtures from the canvas_ai_test module to simulate AI responses in a predictable way.</p>",
        "author": {
